#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:5 47d98ea8452e4858810c4540c0b6caf2
msgid ""
"ComfyUI-VoxCPMTTS is a lightweight ComfyUI node for VoxCPM 1.5, featuring "
"built-in **automatic speech recognition** for reference audio transcription."
msgstr "ComfyUI-VoxCPMTTS 是面向 VoxCPM 1.5 的轻量 ComfyUI 节点，内置参考音频的 **自动语音识别** 转写。"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:7 24757b57132e49afb12c951778df0a30
msgid ""
"Repo: `1038lab/ComfyUI-VoxCPMTTS <https://github.com/1038lab/ComfyUI-"
"VoxCPMTTS>`_"
