msgid "**AILab_VoxCPMTTS** — simplified node with hidden advanced parameters"
msgstr "**AILab_VoxCPMTTS** — 简化节点，高级参数默认隐藏"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:26 e7ae3422ada44087a27e8ce34f290102
msgid "**AILab_VoxCPMTTS_Advanced** — full control over all generation parameters"
msgstr "**AILab_VoxCPMTTS_Advanced** — 可手动控制全部生成参数"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:29 1440b9f1cd914620b78150a8c91ee42a
msgid "Features"
msgstr "主要特性"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:31 a3bea13f771742a586e0708283af8d92
msgid ""
"TTS and voice cloning with **VoxCPM 1.5** (44.1 kHz output); VoxCPM 0.5B "
"also available in the UI"
msgstr "基于 **VoxCPM 1.5** 的 TTS 与声音克隆（44.1 kHz 输出）；界面中也可选用 VoxCPM 0.5B"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:32 37ada0e89b864ef5a410bc0855c18010
msgid ""
"**Auto-transcription** of reference audio via faster-whisper (requires "
"enabling ``auto_transcribe_reference``)"
msgstr "通过 faster-whisper 对参考音频 **自动转写** （需启用 ``auto_transcribe_reference``）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:33 9e178ec5b5d84e2ea1075394f2aa5ee8
msgid ""
"Fade-in post-processing for smoother audio output (configurable "
"``fade_in_ms`` on Advanced node)"
msgstr "淡入后处理使输出更顺滑（高级节点可配置 ``fade_in_ms``）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:34 0ef71e730c604620b6fea723700c7597
msgid ""
"Simplified node uses fixed defaults (``cfg_value=2.0``, "
"``inference_steps=10``); Advanced node exposes full manual control"
msgstr "简化节点固定默认（``cfg_value=2.0``、``inference_steps=10``）；高级节点可完全手动调节"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:35 8397a326ccd842ab9f1ea45f0385175d
msgid "``REFERENCE_TEXT`` output port for inspecting ASR results"
msgstr "``REFERENCE_TEXT`` 输出端口用于查看 ASR 结果"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:36 f0c4f1d9bb514879838aa2417497ba1f
msgid ""
"Configurable ASR model via environment variable ``VOXCPM_ASR_MODEL`` "
"(``tiny`` / ``small`` / ``medium`` / ``large``)"
msgstr ""
"通过环境变量 ``VOXCPM_ASR_MODEL`` 配置 ASR 模型（``tiny`` / ``small`` / ``medium`` / "
"``large``）"

#: ../../integrations/comfyui_voxcpmtts.rst:37 36507cc48cb04c86b81ff1678589cb3f
msgid "Multi-device: **auto** (auto-detect), **CUDA**, **MPS**, **CPU**"
msgstr "多设备： **auto** （自动检测）、**CUDA**、**MPS**、**CPU**"

